{"id": "1497812127568625684", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "516998769888329749", "author_name": "zzzorz", "author_bot": false, "content": "これから作れる〜というのは、最強チームは何か、と読み替えても大丈夫そうですかね？", "timestamp": "2026-04-26T04:10:39.216000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1497812484126670960", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "516998769888329749", "author_name": "zzzorz", "author_bot": false, "content": "現状、コラボや再販なしのキャラがないので、復刻を待てば組むことが可能です。", "timestamp": "2026-04-26T04:12:04.226000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1497833422272331847", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "336149234849939458", "author_name": "kyotera", "author_bot": false, "content": "既出だったら申し訳ないのですが、アイテム交換の優先度を教えてほしいです！！\n薔薇金券は買えるだけ買って、澱と勲章はコアのみ交換済み。供物と珠は全未交換状態です。\n課金額は月15000くらいに収めたいと考えてます！！\n魔法瓶や輪転の書は一切手を付けてません！！", "timestamp": "2026-04-26T05:35:16.269000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1497839780027695146", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "763468659863584799", "author_name": "sugoitsubasanohaetaop", "author_bot": false, "content": "絶対に買っときたいってのはこれくらいだと思います", "timestamp": "2026-04-26T06:00:32.076000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1497839778618413219", "filename": "Screenshot_20260426-145933.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1797056, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1400058619726266462/1497839778618413219/Screenshot_20260426-145933.png?ex=6a33897f&is=6a3237ff&hm=fc93a79589551df724c83675b0fd3fd2db06748ed2fb66b01454e81da4d0a2a8&"}, {"id": "1497839779197354034", "filename": "Screenshot_20260426-145945.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1832481, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1400058619726266462/1497839779197354034/Screenshot_20260426-145945.png?ex=6a33897f&is=6a3237ff&hm=f8893ca173c861a21be578502a5f61f45d08b5aa268657dbcf5b4b8f93f39aac&"}, {"id": "1497839779860189275", "filename": "Screenshot_20260426-145951.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1894741, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1400058619726266462/1497839779860189275/Screenshot_20260426-145951.png?ex=6a338980&is=6a323800&hm=948f6d668cfc5a75bc8682f0abcdc6322458c1d888875b93a228d05bf0fa72ca&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1497841023345233950", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "763468659863584799", "author_name": "sugoitsubasanohaetaop", "author_bot": false, "content": "交換出来るキャラについては\nドール…今でも出番ある\nオジール…キャラ揃うと出番あんま無い\nロータン…orz\nアイギス…ピンポイントで欲しい場面はそこそこある\nオレッタ…好きな人が多くよく使われるが、活躍させたいなら編成が限定キャラ多く含む\nエリカ…超次元やるならコンテンツによってはよく使われる", "timestamp": "2026-04-26T06:05:28.506000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1497841756409040967", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 19, "author_id": "336149234849939458", "author_name": "kyotera", "author_bot": false, "content": "丁寧にありがとうございます！！！\nわかりやすい！！！\nコアは割と取っちゃって良いんですね...札とかにリソース割いた方がいいのかな～？って思ってたので助かります！！", "timestamp": "2026-04-26T06:08:23.282000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["763468659863584799"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1497839780027695146", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1497843252047511632", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "763468659863584799", "author_name": "sugoitsubasanohaetaop", "author_bot": false, "content": "ガチャポン引いてる時がやっぱり楽しいので私は絶対コア買ってます()\n手持ちが揃ってきても使う札はスクショで上げたのくらいになるとは思います。\n融災禁区ってコンテンツがもう解放されているかは分からないですが、序盤は札揃ってなくて困ることもあるのでその時は各種札も交換を視野に入れた方が良いかもです。", "timestamp": "2026-04-26T06:14:19.870000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🙇", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}, {"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
